* MOSFET CS amplifier
VDD vdd 0 DC 19.88
Vin in 0 AC 1
Cin in gate 15u
RG1 vdd gate 820k
RG2 gate 0 270k
RD vdd drain 8.2k
M1 drain gate source 0 NMOS1
RS source 0 3.3k
Cout drain out 1u
Rload out 0 82k
.model NMOS1 NMOS (Level=1 VTO=2.0 KP=1.0e-3 L=2e-6 W=50e-6 Lambda=0.0 Gamma=0.0 Phi=0.6)
.ac dec 50 10 10Meg
.print ac V(out)
.end